  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction à Kdebindings</title>

    <para>Kdebindings fournit la capacité à écrire des applications <application>KDE</application>
    dans des lanqages différents incluant <application>Ruby</application>, 
    <application>Perl</application>, <application>Python</application>, 
    <application>Java</application>, <application>JavaScript</application>, 
    <application>C#</application>, et <application>Smoke</application>.</para>

    &lfs67_checked;

